 Studios Florida]]\n|1990\n|\n|-\n|[[List of former Universal Studios Florida attractions#The Boneyard|The Boneyard]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|1990\n|Closed in 2008\n|-\n|[[The Funtastic World of Hanna-Barbera Arena Show|The Funtastic World of Hanna-Barbera]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|1990\n|Closed in 2002\n|-\n|[[List of former Universal Studios Florida attractions#The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle Show|The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle Show]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|1992\n|Closed in 1993\n|-\n|[[List of former Universal Studios Florida attractions#Alfred Hitchcock: The Art of Making Movies|Alfred Hitchcock: The Art of Making Movies]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|1990\n|Closed in 2003\n|-\n|[[A Day in the Park with Barney]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|1995\n|\n|-\n|The Eighth Voyage of [[Sinbad the Sailor|Sinbad]]\n|[[Islands of Adventure]]\n|1999\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Fear Factor Live]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2005\n| rowspan=\"2\" |\n|-\n|[[Universal Studios Hollywood]]\n|-\n|[[Universal 360: A Cinesphere Spectacular]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|2006\n|\n|-\n|[[Creature from the Black Lagoon: The Musical]]\n|[[Universal Studios Hollywood]]\n|2009\n|Co-produced with [[Broadway Attractions]]\n|-\n|[[Special Effects Stage]]\n|[[Universal Studios Hollywood]]\n|2010\n|\n|-\n|[[Lights! Camera! Action! Hosted by Steven Spielberg]]\n|[[Universal Studios Singapore]]\n|2010\n|\n|-\n|[[Universal's Cinematic Spectacular: 100 Years of Movie Memories]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|2012\n|\n|}\n\n==== Roller coasters ====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Project\n!Park/Resort\n!Opening Date\n!Notes\n|-\n|[[Dragon Challenge]]\n|[[Islands of Adventure]]\n|1999, 2010\n|Previously known as Dueling Dragons, co-produced with [[Warner Bros.]] Recreation Group\n|-\n|[[The Incredible Hulk Coaster]]\n|[[Islands of Adventure]]\n|1999\n|Co-produced with [[Marvel Entertainment]]\n|-\n|[[Woody Woodpecker's Nuthouse Coaster]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|1999\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Flight of the Hippogriff]]\n|[[Islands of Adventure]]\n|2000, 2010\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Previously known as The Flying Unicorn, co-produced with [[Warner Bros.]] Recreation Group\n|-\n|[[Universal Studios Japan]]\n|2014\n|-\n|[[Universal Studios Hollywood]]\n|2016\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Revenge of the Mummy]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|2004\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Co-production with Alphaville\n|-\n|[[Universal Studios Hollywood]]\n|2004\n|-\n|[[Universal Studios Singapore]]\n|2010\n|-\n|''[[Hollywood Rip Ride Rockit]]''\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|2009\n|Ride manufacturer [[Maurer Sohne]]\n|-\n|''[[Hollywood Dream \u2013 The Ride]]''\n|[[Universal Studios Japan]]\n|2007\n|Ride manufacturer [[Bolliger & Mabillard]]\n|-\n|''[[Space Fantasy \u2013 The Ride]]''\n|[[Universal Studios Japan]]\n|2010\n|Ride manufacturer [[Mack Rides]]\n|}\n\n== Awards ==\n\n=== [[Themed Entertainment Association|Thea]] Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.teaconnect.org/Blog/Thea-Blog/index.cfm?id=2261|title=Past Thea Award recipients: 1994-2017|work=teaconnect.org|access-date=2017-09-20|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111192454/http://www.teaconnect.org/Blog/THEA-Blog/index.cfm?id=2261|archivedate=2015-01-11}}</ref> ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Award\n!Year(s) Received\n!Project\n!Park/Resort\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |Paragon Award\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2015\n|[[The Wizarding World of Harry Potter]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n|[[Diagon alley|Diagon Alley]]\n|-\n|[[Hogwarts Express (Universal Orlando Resort)|Hogwarts Express]]\n|-\n|[[Diagon alley|Diagon Alley Retail/Dining]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"23\" |Award for Outstanding Achievement\n|1996\n|[[Waterworld: A Live Sea War Spectacular]]\n|[[Universal Studios Hollywood]]\n|-\n|1997\n|[[T2 3-D: Battle Across Time|Terminator 2:3D: The Battle Across Time]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |200