 Ride]]''\n|[[Universal Studios Japan]]\n|2010\n|Ride manufacturer [[Mack Rides]]\n|}\n\n== Awards ==\n\n=== [[Themed Entertainment Association|Thea]] Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.teaconnect.org/Blog/Thea-Blog/index.cfm?id=2261|title=Past Thea Award recipients: 1994-2017|work=teaconnect.org|access-date=2017-09-20|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111192454/http://www.teaconnect.org/Blog/THEA-Blog/index.cfm?id=2261|archivedate=2015-01-11}}</ref> ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Award\n!Year(s) Received\n!Project\n!Park/Resort\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |Paragon Award\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2015\n|[[The Wizarding World of Harry Potter]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n|[[Diagon alley|Diagon Alley]]\n|-\n|[[Hogwarts Express (Universal Orlando Resort)|Hogwarts Express]]\n|-\n|[[Diagon alley|Diagon Alley Retail/Dining]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"23\" |Award for Outstanding Achievement\n|1996\n|[[Waterworld: A Live Sea War Spectacular]]\n|[[Universal Studios Hollywood]]\n|-\n|1997\n|[[T2 3-D: Battle Across Time|Terminator 2:3D: The Battle Across Time]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2000\n|FiestAventura\n|[[PortAventura Park|Universal Studios Port Aventura]]\n|-\n|[[The Amazing Adventures of Spider-Man]]\n|[[Islands of Adventure]]\n|-\n|2001\n|[[Men in Black: Alien Attack]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n|2002\n|Animal Celebration\n|[[Universal Studios Japan]]\n|-\n|2002\n|Templo del Fuego\n|[[PortAventura Park|Universal Studios Port Aventura]]\n|-\n|2005\n|[[Revenge of the Mummy]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n|2006\n|[[Fear Factor Live]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n|2008\n|Peter Pan's Neverland\n|[[Universal Studios Japan]]\n|-\n|2009\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[The Simpsons Ride]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n|2009\n|[[Universal Studios Hollywood]]\n|-\n|2010\n|[[Disaster!]]\n|[[Universal Studios Florida]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2011\n|[[The Wizarding World of Harry Potter]]\n|[[Islands of Adv